[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9442] changed the nightly build schedule make it start by 9:15 BeiJing Time
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9441] fixed cleanup of nightly build workflow
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9433] fixed the cleanup of old nightly releases
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9432] Use Nushell v0.81 for release workflows
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9430] Synchronize code before the nightly build starts
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9423] Fix removal of old nightly releases
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9422] Try to make a nightly release by workflow
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9414] Reset .github/workflows/release-pkg.nu
alkhatib 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9440] fixed clippy errors (Mac)
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9431] http post --content-type should set Content-Type header
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9436] allowed comments in multiple line pipeline
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9399] disable bracketed paste during evaluation
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9377] ``save``
 command: Don't use BufWriter to write external strem to a file
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9368] don't allow 
``save``
 command to save both stdout and stderr to the same file
hanjunghyuk 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9427] removed ZB and ZiB from file size type
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9426] updated ini dependency
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9424] updated dfr to polars 0.30.0
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9420] allow empty string arguments
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9416] allow paths to have brackets
FilipAndersson245 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9415] changed global allocator to mimalloc, improving performance.
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9391] Changes HashMap to use aHash instead, giving a performance boost.
Mehrbod2002 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9407] renamed uid to user column in ls --long
ja-cop 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9402] added "regex" search term to commands with regex functionality
amtoine 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9398] simplified the declaration of extra commands
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9392] added a comment note to the PR template about linking issues
AstrickHarren 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9397] fixed find puts extra cols into record
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9395] Add 
``zip-into-record``
 to std iter
tarunsamanta2k20 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9357] completed the install command to install plugins #9342
Yethal 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9355] refactored test-runner to no longer require tests to be exported
zhiburt 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9341] bumped tabled to 0.12.1
stevenxxiu 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9031] merged 
``repl_buffer_state``
, 
``repl_cursor_pos``
 into one mutex
